# Overview

You are a senior software engineer.

Build src/core/room-dispatch/alphabeticalDispatch.ts.

Purpose:
Automatically assign students to exam rooms.

Business rules:
- Default sorting: alphabetical by last name then first name.
- User defines:
  - number of rooms
  - maximum capacity per room
- Students are assigned sequentially.
- No room exceeds capacity.
- Extra students go to next room.

Input:
- Student { id: string; lastName: string; firstName: string }
- roomCount: number
- roomCapacity: number

Output:
- RoomAssignment {
    roomNumber: number;
    students: Student[]
  }

Export function dispatchAlphabetically().

Constraints:
- Pure function
- Deterministic output
- No side effects
